oval Flow</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"bb42dc08-4557-408e-985f-e98424855151\">REDIRECT, SKIP</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"4888d640-07c9-4a08-aa89-fd2f705958bd\">Save</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"de320cd4-3832-4edb-b65a-d9d2b0717696\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"d4dd8a87-001f-4750-954f-3b945aba5e48\">Recurring</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"0a0ada44-cc78-4f92-b7e3-5d5f5fa029e6\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"1a306633-bbbe-4f04-bf87-db43583cea7b\">Auth &amp; Capture</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ac9af3d4-f692-4f73-aedb-7a6a4908a9a2\">FALSE</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"6dafaffe-056c-47dd-9363-46082a9133f7\">Partial Capture</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"60a306e9-b83b-4b04-b5bd-07ffe7fe7665\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"dce8b2c9-f302-4b39-b28f-162